content: nulLeeKH: Merged two significant PRs: #1487 adding a code of conduct (+13.8k/-6.5k lines) and #1433 fixing the Twitter client search feature (+40k/-31.3k lines), while also proposing a parse_mode selection feature for the Telegram client in PR #1458. Created two proposals for setting up lint/prettier and husky (issues #1459 and #1486), both of which were closed. Contributed actively to the project through 7 code reviews with comments and made substantial code changes across 1932 files (+71.4k/-44.6k lines) in 27 commits, with activity concentrated on just 5 days this month.
